				<td colspan="2"><span>This was the GAYEST online game I have ever played! The graphics were HORRIBLE. If you melee a mob, your screen &quot;locks on&quot; to it and you cant look anywhere else. I played the entire free trial and only saw like 3-4 different mobs types. Everything was like LDoN...same repetative crap over and over. Also, make sure you call those bastards when you get sick of the free trial or they are going to charge your credit card.
<br />

<br />
I give this game a BIG FAT &quot;F&quot; . The only redeeming quality was the ability to play as a dragon, but even that sucked as it was broken and you stayed as a hatchling dragon no matter what level you were.
<br />

<br />
It also had no role-playing qualities whatsoever. Its hard to get immersed into a game when there are actual signs that say &quot;this way to monsters&quot; or &quot;this way to trade skills components&quot;.
<br />

<br />
Oh, and the way you handle quests and item manipulation are horrid. You cant even hand an item to an npc or player. 
<br />

<br />
Don't even think about swimming. The water isnt even animated at all, and swimming consists of falling straight to the ocean bottom and walking at 1/2 speed until you drown.
<br />

<br />
Also, theres no falling damage. How realistic can a game be when you jump off a 500 ft cliff and take no damage? You dont even bounce...you land on your feet like a housecat.
<br />

<br />
Did I mention the graphics were horrible?
<br />

<br />
Oh, the lag too....I went Linkdead at LEAST once an hour.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%"><IMG SRC="http://www.hometown.aol.com/mudplayerx/images/theslums.gif ">
</span></td>
